### ğŸš€ **Basic Node.js Commands**

| Purpose                            | Command                     |
| ---------------------------------- | --------------------------- |
| Run a Node.js file                 | `node filename.js`          |
| Check Node version                 | `node -v`                   |
| Open Node REPL (interactive shell) | `node`                      |
| Exit Node REPL                     | `.exit` or `Ctrl + C` twice |

---

### ğŸ“¦ **NPM (Node Package Manager) Commands**

| Purpose                  | Command                                         |
| ------------------------ | ----------------------------------------------- |
| Check npm version        | `npm -v`                                        |
| Initialize a project     | `npm init` *(or `npm init -y` to skip prompts)* |
| Install a package        | `npm install <package>` or `npm i <package>`    |
| Install a dev dependency | `npm install <package> --save-dev`              |
| Uninstall a package      | `npm uninstall <package>`                       |
| List installed packages  | `npm list`                                      |
| Update all packages      | `npm update`                                    |

---

### ğŸ“ **Project Setup & Scripts**

| Purpose                            | Command                                      |
| ---------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------- |
| Run a script (from `package.json`) | `npm run <script-name>`                      |
| Run `start` script                 | `npm start` *(shortcut for `npm run start`)* |
| Run `test` script                  | `npm test` *(shortcut for `npm run test`)*   |

---

### ğŸ§ª **Useful Tools**

| Tool                                 | Install                                        | Run                                |
| ------------------------------------ | ---------------------------------------------- | ---------------------------------- |
| **Nodemon** *(auto-restarts server)* | `npm install -g nodemon`                       | `nodemon filename.js`              |
| **ESLint** *(linter)*                | `npm install eslint --save-dev`                | `npx eslint yourfile.js`           |
| **Prettier** *(code formatter)*      | `npm install --save-dev --save-exact prettier` | `npx prettier --write yourfile.js` |

---

### ğŸ§° **Common Node.js Modules**

```js
const fs = require('fs');         // File system
